---
const sessions = [
  {
    number: 'Session One',
    title: 'Your Data Decoded',
    duration: '30 min with Chris',
    description:
      'A one-on-one with Chris, Halo founder, walking through your genetic profile and bloodwork. What your markers mean, how they connect to how you feel, and what they suggest for your body specifically. You leave with a personalized protocol: nutrition, movement, and supplements built on your actual biology.',
    borderClass: 'border-nwprt-sky/60',
  },
  {
    number: 'Session Two',
    title: 'Your Body Explained',
    duration: '30–45 min with the MD',
    description:
      "A one-on-one with the affiliated functional medicine doctor, a women's health specialist who has already reviewed your bloodwork panel before you sit down. Your hormone levels, metabolic markers, and what they mean for how you actually feel day to day. Clear, honest answers to the questions your regular doctor has never had time to fully address.",
    borderClass: 'border-nwprt-yellow/80',
  },
  {
    number: 'Session Three',
    title: 'Your Deep Dive',
    duration: '30 min · Your choice',
    description:
      'You select your specialist based on the health areas you submitted in your intake form. Your expert is fully prepared for your conversation before you arrive.',
    borderClass: 'border-nwprt-pink/60',
    options: ['Nutrition and longevity', 'Fitness and movement', 'Mental clarity and stress', 'Sleep optimization'],
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-nwprt-off-white text-nwprt-navy py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="scroll-reveal">
      <div class="caption text-nwprt-navy/50 mb-3">Chapter two</div>
      <h2 class="display text-4xl md:text-6xl text-nwprt-navy mb-6">Your Science Sessions</h2>
      <div class="rule bg-nwprt-navy mb-10 opacity-40"></div>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-nwprt-navy/80 mb-12">
        <p>
          Your genetic data and bloodwork are reviewed before you arrive. Your sessions are built around
          what they reveal. You are not sitting in a lecture designed for someone else &mdash; you are in a
          room with experts who already know your biology.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Before You Arrive — two flavor cards */}
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-nwprt-navy p-8 border-l-4 border-nwprt-yellow">
          <div class="caption text-nwprt-yellow mb-3">Before You Arrive</div>
          <h3 class="display text-2xl text-nwprt-cream mb-4">Your Genetic Kit</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-nwprt-cream/80">
            A few weeks before you arrive, a Halo genetic kit is shipped to your home. A simple saliva
            swab under five minutes and a prepaid return envelope. By the time you walk through the door,
            the experts already know your biology.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-nwprt-navy/15 p-8 border-l-4 border-nwprt-sky/60">
          <div class="caption text-nwprt-navy/60 mb-3">Also Before Arrival</div>
          <h3 class="display text-2xl text-nwprt-navy mb-4">Your Bloodwork</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-nwprt-navy/75">
            Your bloodwork is coordinated before arrival through a private MD link. You either upload
            recent labs or complete a new panel at a lab near you. This is not a standard annual physical
            &mdash; it is a comprehensive functional medicine panel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Three sessions */}
      <div class="space-y-6">
        {sessions.map((session) => (
          <div class={`bg-white border border-nwprt-navy/10 p-6 md:p-8 border-l-4 ${session.borderClass}`}>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-6">
              <div>
                <div class="caption text-nwprt-navy/50 mb-2">{session.number}</div>
                <h3 class="display text-xl md:text-2xl text-nwprt-navy mb-2">{session.title}</h3>
                <div class="text-xs text-nwprt-navy/50">{session.duration}</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-nwprt-navy/75 mb-4">{session.description}</p>
                {session.options && (
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mt-4">
                    {session.options.map((option) => (
                      <div class="text-xs px-3 py-2 bg-nwprt-off-white text-nwprt-navy/60 border border-nwprt-navy/10">
                        {option}
                      </div>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                )}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-nwprt-navy p-6 border-l-4 border-nwprt-sky/60">
        <p class="text-sm text-nwprt-cream/75 leading-relaxed">
          Additional sessions are available to purchase during the program. Many women find one
          conversation opens three more questions they want answered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
